name: Doll Steak
description:
~ Celebrating my first 500 followers on Twitter ~

This artwork titled 'Doll Steak' because when I draw this, I listen to Nirvana's Milk It (In Utero), the night before I draw it, I'm watching Montage of Heck. The day I draw it, I'm always remember Kurt's doodle, and finally I re-make it in my own way. Marker on A5 Paper. Scanned.
